This exam was dictated at Endeavor Health Swedish Hospital.
Exam: MAMMO SCREENING BILATERAL - DIGITAL. Direct digital imaging using CAD. Tomosynthesis images were obtained and reviewed.
Clinical History: Screening. Per the modified Gail model, lifetime risk of breast malignancy is 8.8%.
Technique: Two standard digital views of both breasts were performed and reviewed with the aid of R2 CAD. Tomosynthesis images were obtained and reviewed.
The breasts are almost entirely fatty.
There are no suspicious masses, microcalcifications or areas of nonsurgical architectural distortion.
There are no breast arterial calcifications.
